<br>
As they passed, she pointed out the vastness of the pastures. Even though it had begun snowing higher up in the mountians, and indeed, there was even some snow in the village, the grass was still green from the Summer. <br>
<br>
She kept walking, and they eventually ended up at the Dining Hall. <br>
